	<description><![CDATA[Jms Multi Sites article content sharing.<br/>
This component allows to display the content (section, categories, articles) coming from any websites defined in Joomla Multi Sites.<br/>
There is no administration to manage the content of the websites. To update the sections, categories and articles, use the standard Joomla content menu or similar tools.<br/>
<br/>
Version 1.1.1 is compatible with Joomla 1.5 AND 1.6.<br/>
Version 1.1.2 is compatible with Joomla 1.5 AND 1.7.<br/>
Version 1.1.3 add in section layout under Joomla 1.5 the possibility to select the number of artcile to display like under joomla 1.7<br/>
Version 1.1.3 add in section layout under Joomla 1.5 the possibility to show or hide the filter and the select display dropdown<br/>
Version 1.1.5 fix joomla 2.5 compatibility<br/>
]]></description>
